    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is ready to hit the pavement for its next owner! I\u2019d love for this to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
