      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering high-revving power through six individual throttle bodies. Mechanically sorted, it boasts a recently serviced VANOS system and documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a vital preventative measure for this chassis. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension maintains factory geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative. A mechanically sound example ready for the enthusiast driver.",
